data.description: Looking for 1 level living? This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath custom ranch is just what you are looking for. Hardwood floors throughout 1st floor,living room offers a warm & inviting floor to ceiling stone fireplace for those chilly nights. Dining area with door leading to a huge 3 season room. Spacious kitchen with plenty of cabinet & counter space.Large primary bedroom with primary bath. Family room with brick fireplace on lower level. Plenty of parking in your 2 car garage. Kick back & enjoy a cup of coffee on your covered front porch. Close to Taconic Parkway, I-84 & Shopping
